@startuml v2x_priority_arbitration_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title V2X Priority Arbitration Signal Flow\n(TEST_SCN / external ingress -> V2X -> ADAS / IVI)

actor "Emergency Sources\n(TEST_SCN / network ingress)" as Source #F4F7FB
participant "V2X\ningress arbitration owner" as V2X #E8F7E8
participant "ADAS\nemergency risk consumer" as ADAS #FCE8FF
participant "IVI\nrender / sound consumer" as IVI #E8F0FE

== Candidate Ingress ==

Source -> V2X : emergency type / status / sourceId / eta / direction
activate V2X
V2X -> V2X : stageEmergencyIngress()
V2X -> V2X : isHigherPriority(newType, newEta, newSourceId,\nactiveType, activeEta, activeSourceId)
note right of V2X
Priority rule
- ambulance > police
- shorter ETA first
- lower sourceId on tie
end note

== Active Emergency Selection ==

V2X -> V2X : select active emergency context
V2X -> V2X : publishNormalizedEmergencyIngress()
V2X -> V2X : publishActiveEmergencyToV2X()
V2X -> V2X : pushEmergencyMonitor()
V2X -> ADAS : Core::emergencyContext
V2X -> ADAS : CoreState::emergencyIngressDirection
V2X -> ADAS : CoreState::emergencyIngressEtaSec
V2X -> ADAS : Core::timeoutClear
V2X -> IVI : V2X::v2xFrame
note right of V2X
Representative outputs
- emergencyContext
- emergencyIngressDirection
- emergencyIngressEtaSec
- timeoutClear
- v2xFrame
end note
deactivate V2X

== Downstream Consumers ==

activate ADAS
V2X -> ADAS : normalized ingress seams
ADAS -> ADAS : calcProximityRisk()
deactivate ADAS

activate IVI
V2X -> IVI : v2xFrame / emergency context mirror
IVI -> IVI : render emergency warning / sound state
deactivate IVI

note over Source, IVI
Representative runtime chain
1. Multiple emergency candidates arrive
2. V2X arbitrates by type, ETA, and sourceId
3. V2X publishes one normalized active emergency context
4. ADAS and IVI consume the same selected ingress
end note

@enduml
